[{"Id": 1019962, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Reza (a) said: Whoever makes it a habit to recite these two names regularly will get a long life, will rule over the hearts and will be a favourite figure are two names from the Majestic names of Allah, the Exalted, but as they are recited together, they are counted as one...", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Reza (a) farmate hai: Jis kisi ne bhi in do (2) naamo ko rozaana padhne ki aadat bana li, to usey lampi umr ataa hogi, logo’n ke dilo’n par hukumat karne aur logo’n ke darmiyaan mein pasandidah hoga. Hai to yeh Allah (swt) ke do naam, magar jab saath mein padha jaayega to woh ek shumaar hoga…", "UrduDescription": "امام رضاؑ فرماتے ہیں: جس کسی نے بھی ان دو ناموں کو روزانہ پڑھنے کی عادت بنا لی، تو اُسے تویل عمر عطا ہوگی، لوگوں کے دلوں پر حکومت کرنے اور لوگوں کے درمیان میں پسندیدہ ہو گا، تو یہ اللہ کے دو نام، مگر جب ساتھ میں پڑھا جائے تو وہ ایک شمار ہو گا۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9